                    "title": "Safety Plan Review and Modification (End of Session)",
                    "therapeutic_goal": "Ensure the safety plan is up-to-date and effective.",
                    "explanation_of_technique": "Review the safety plan with the client and make any necessary modifications. Ensure that the client has access to the resources listed in the safety plan and knows how to use them. Emphasize the importance of reaching out for help when needed. This is a crucial step in the 'End of Session'."
                }
            ]
        },
        {
